snippet.title: two at once - Texas AMBER Alert (EAS #124)
snippet.description:
Two AMBER Alerts were issued. Both Children were found safe. I only caught one of the AMBER Alerts though. 

NWR Stations, Broadcast Stations, or Cable Systems: WXK38 Amarillo [Streamed], WXK26 Laredo, and Spectrum Cable.

BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE CORPUS CHRISTI TX
652 PM CDT MON JUN 8 2020

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT
NETWORK 

THE PORT ARTHUR POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR JASON ROBERTS,
BLACK, MALE, 7 MONTHS OLD, HEIGHT 2 FEET, WEIGHT 27 POUNDS, BLACK
HAIR, BROWN EYES, AND LAST SEEN WEARING A GRAY ONESIE.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR NATHAN LYNN ROBERTS JUNIOR, BLACK, MALE, 26
YEARS OLD, HEIGHT 5 FEET 10 INCHES, WEIGHT 178 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR,
BROWN EYES AND LAST SEEN WEARING A BLACK MUSCLE SHIRT AND BLACK
PANTS, IN CONNECTION WITH HIS ABDUCTION. 

THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A GOLD TAN JEEP CHEROKEE WITH AN UNKNOWN
LICENSE PLATE.

THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN PORT ARTHUR, TEXAS. 

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER.  

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE PORT
ARTHUR POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 4 0 9 9 8 3 8 6 0 1.

$$

Local Forecast (Elevator) - Kevin MacLeod
